    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ジュード</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Jude</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>30</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あぁ！？
どういう意味だよ、ソリャ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh?! Heck do you mean by that?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>言葉の通りの意味だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I mean exactly what I said.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>世界樹には私達が向かう。
お前達は引き返せ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We're heading for the World Tree.
You two need to go back.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>え、で、でも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? B-But...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ミラ、もうちょっと言い方が……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Milla, you should have tried
saying that a little nicer...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>30</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>気に入らねェなぁ。
まるでオレ達じゃ
世界樹に辿り着けねェみたいに聞こえんぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't like that. Sounds to me like you're sayin'
we ain't gonna make it to the World Tree.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ああ、そう言ったつもりだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes, that is what I'm saying.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>上等だ！
だったらそれが思い上がりだって事
お前に教えてやるよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Fine then! We'll just have to teach ya
not to make assumptions about us!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>私達と戦うつもりか？
いいだろう。
その代わり、負けたら諦めるんだぞ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You mean to fight us? Very well.
In exchange, if you lose, you give up on this.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>31</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>やってやろうじゃねぇか！
んな事にはなんねぇけどな！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I wanna see you try!
It ain't happenin'!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>21</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
